data.purpose: LEMON TREE HOTELS LIMITED has informed the Exchange about Board Meeting to be held on 14-Nov-2024 to consider and approve the Half Yearly Unaudited Financial results of the Company for the period ended September 2024 and Other business.

LEMON TREE HOTELS LIMITED has informed the Exchange about Board Meeting to be held on 14-Nov-2024 to consider and approve the Half Yearly Unaudited Financial results of the Company for the period ended September 2024 and Other business.
To consider and approve the Unaudited  financial results (Standalone & Consolidated ) for the period ended September 30, 2024
To consider and approve the financial results for the period ended Jun 30, 2024 and other business matters
To consider and approve the financial results for the period ended March 31, 2024 and other business matters
